BFF}",{"title":172,"searchDepth":203,"depth":203,"links":1164},[1165,1166,1167,1168,1169],{"id":14,"depth":203,"text":15},{"id":22,"depth":203,"text":23},{"id":130,"depth":203,"text":131},{"id":155,"depth":203,"text":156},{"id":1145,"depth":203,"text":1146},"React","2022-09-15 00:01:00","No matter what, you've got to start by getting comfortable with React's basic concepts and a bit of its background. That groundwork makes it way easier to spot the differences when you pick up other frameworks later. I'm a Vue developer myself, so I'm writing this with the mindset of someone adding one more framework to the toolbox — which means you'll see a few side-by-side comparisons between Vue and React syntax. Mostly I want to make this an easy on-ramp for fellow Vue devs. Enough preamble, let's get into it.","md","en",{},"\u002Fen\u002Freact\u002Freact-day-01-what-is-react","5",{"title":6,"description":1172},false,"en\u002FReact\u002Freact-day-01-what-is-react",[1182,1183,1184,1185,1186,1187,1188,1189],"You'll Have to Learn React Eventually, So Why Not Now?","React Basics","React Hooks","React Class","Vue","Composition API","Framework","Library",null,"\u002Fen\u002Freact\u002F2022\u002F09\u002F15\u002Freact-day-01-what-is-react\u002F","1C7UL_8FC0QaPie3-Ys6vXC-mbTQKaYZ2xKzlpWOMrA",{"newer":1194,"older":1198},{"url":1195,"title":1196,"date":1197},"\u002Fen\u002Freact\u002F2022\u002F09\u002F16\u002Freact-day-02-hello-react\u002F","You'll Learn React Eventually, So Why Not Now? — React Basics: Hello React (2)","2022-09-16 00:01:29",{"url":1199,"title":1200,"date":1201},"\u002Fen\u002Flearning\u002F2022\u002F09\u002F12\u002Fdunning-kruger-effect-explained\u002F","What Is the Dunning–Kruger Effect? Thought You Knew It, But Actually Didn't","2022-09-12 10:51:48",[1203,1208,1213],{"url":1204,"title":1205,"date":1206,"readingMinutes":1207},"\u002Fen\u002Freact\u002F2022\u002F10\u002F14\u002Flearn-react-now-30-wrap-up-and-toc\u002F","Learn React Now — Wrap-up Notes & Full Table of Contents (30)","2022-10-14 00:00:01","4",{"url":1209,"title":1210,"date":1211,"readingMinutes":1212},"\u002Fen\u002Freact\u002F2022\u002F10\u002F13\u002Flearn-react-29-react-redux-quick-start\u002F","Learn React Eventually, So Why Not Now? - React Redux: Redux and a Quick Start - (29)","2022-10-13 00:00:01","6",{"url":1214,"title":1215,"date":1216,"readingMinutes":1207},"\u002Fen\u002Freact\u002F2022\u002F10\u002F12\u002Freact-day-28-router-lazy-loading\u002F","Why Learn React Eventually? Learn It Now! - React Router Lazy Loading (28)","2022-10-12 00:00:01",1784087341497]